Convenient storage: The brush handle is made of nonslip rubber material, providing a comfortable grip; The dustpan and broom adopt a buckle type and suspension hole design, which is convenient for storage and hanging to save space.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Durable Small Dustpan and Brush Set
reviews.reviewText: The brush is made using durable bristles. They will not scratch the surfaces it is used on. The dustpan has soft rubber edges that adhere to the surface it is used on. It helps to keep any swept-up trash from falling off the pan. It is a nice-sized dustpan, and the color is an attractive ocean blue. This set is suitable for small spaces. The broom can clean gaps and small areas. It is easy to use, and the broom has a comfortable anti-slip rubber handle. It is a well-constructed dustpan and broom set. The broom can be stored in the dustpan handle. I am very pleased with it. I recommend it.
